[SPEAKER_00] koji grade crkvu,

680
00:37:31,659 --> 00:37:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] složna braća crkvu grade.

681
00:37:33,159 --> 00:37:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo recimo

682
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:35,280
[SPEAKER_00] složeni brak

683
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji je obitelj gradi

684
00:37:36,539 --> 00:37:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je jako,

685
00:37:37,039 --> 00:37:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] jako bitno.

686
00:37:37,679 --> 00:37:39,219
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo složno društvo

687
00:37:39,219 --> 00:37:40,239
[SPEAKER_00] koje gradi jednu državu

688
00:37:40,239 --> 00:37:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] i slično

689
00:37:40,679 --> 00:37:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] i to je iznimno poučno.

690
00:37:42,039 --> 00:37:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Neka to bude

691
00:37:43,039 --> 00:37:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] evo poruka za kraj

692
00:37:44,119 --> 00:37:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] o složnosti braće

693
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,179
[SPEAKER_00] koji zajedno izgrađuju

694
00:37:47,179 --> 00:37:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] jednostrednu budućnost

